  "title": "Beauty Advisor (Skincare, 5 days)",
  "description": "<p><em>Our client is dermatology clinic with different branches in Singapore.</em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide expert advice to customers on skincare and beauty products. </li>\n  <li>Answer questions and offer personalized recommendations based on customer needs and preferences.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that products are well-organized, stocked, and displayed in a visually appealing manner. </li>\n  <li>Build relationships with customers and follow up on purchases to ensure satisfaction and foster loyalty. </li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma and above.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience in <strong>beauty/skincare retail industry.</strong></li>\n  <li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
